# SSP topology for LNL FPGA with lower DMIC IO clock of 19.2MHz, 2ch PDM1 enabled
"cavs-nocodec\;sof-lnl-nocodec-fpga-2ch-pdm1\;PLATFORM=lnl,NUM_DMICS=2,PDM1_MIC_A_ENABLE=1,\
